OL,3,CSmoke warnings as fire rips through
OL,4,Cindustrial unit
OL,6,FFirefighters worked through the night
OL,7,Fto contain a blaze at an industrial
OL,8,Funit near the centre of Fordingbridge.
OL,10,FLocal residents have been warned to
OL,11,Fkeep their doors and windows closed
OL,12,Fafter fire broke out at the unit on
OL,13,FGreen Lane shortly before 11pm on
OL,14,FSunday, April 5th.
OL,16,FAt its height, nine fire engines and
OL,17,Fan aerial platform attended the scene.
OL,18,FThe intense flames caused the
OL,19,Fbuilding's roof to collapse.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
