OL,3,CSmoke warnings as fire rips through
OL,4,Cindustrial unit
OL,6,FThe fire was brought under control by
OL,7,F2am but crews remained at the scene on
OL,8,FMonday morning.
OL,10,FHampshire & Isle of Wight Fire &
OL,11,FRescue Service said the cause of the
OL,12,Ffire was currently unknown and there
OL,13,Fwere no injuries reported. Road
OL,14,Fclosures are in place on Green Lane
OL,15,Fand Salisbury Road.
